"snippet" : "The Monitor mode offers an extensive collection of metrics. We recommend this mode to monitor enterprise environments. monitor is the default mode. To switch back to the Monitor mode from a different mode, do one of the following: Add the following to the dragent.yaml file and restart the agent: fea...", 
